title: Django Kill... If You Live, Shoot! (Western, 1967) Full Movie | Subtitled

sources.title: Django Kill... If You Live, Shoot! (Western, 1967) Full Movie | Subtitled
sources.description:
Terror from the depths of hell! Various factions, including a half-breed bandit, a gang of homosexual cowboys, and a priest, feud over stolen gold in a surreal town.

Original title:  Se sei vivo spara
Director: Giulio Questi
Writers:  Franco Arcalli, Giulio Questi, María del Carmen Martínez Román
Casting: Tomas Milian, Marilù Tolo, Piero Lulli, Milo Quesada
Genres: Horror, Western
